trans-unit.target: WP New {( source {; option} )} -> Object
creates and returns a 4D Write Pro object
WP Import document ( filePath {; option} ) -> Object
converts an existing 4D Write Pro or 4D Write document (.4wp, .4w7 or .4wt) to a new 4D Write Pro object
WP EXPORT VARIABLE ( wpDoc ; destination ; format {; option} )
exports the wpDoc 4D Write Pro object to the 4D destination variable in the specified format
WP EXPORT DOCUMENT ( wpDoc ; filePath {; format {; option}} )
exports the wpDoc 4D Write Pro object to a document on disk according to the filePath parameter as well as any optional parameters
WP Selection range ( {* ;} wpArea ) -> Object
returns a new range object or a picture object based upon the currently selected content in the wpArea 4D Write Pro area
WP Text range ( targetObj ; startRange ; endRange ) -> Object
returns a new range object containing the selection between startRange and endRange in the targetObj
WP SET ATTRIBUTES ( targetObj ; attribName ; attribValue {; attribName2 ; attribValue2 ; ... ; attribNameN ; attribValueN} )
allows you to set the value of any attribute in a range, element or document
WP PRINT ( wpDoc {; printLayout} )
launches a print job for the 4D Write Pro document specified in wpDoc, or adds the document to the current print job if it is called between OPEN PRINTING JOB and CLOSE PRINTING JOB
WP RESET ATTRIBUTES ( targetObj ; attribName {; attribName2 ; ... ; attribNameN} )
allows you to reset the value of one or more attributes in the range, element, or document passed as parameter
WP GET ATTRIBUTES ( targetObj ; attribName ; attribValue {; attribName2 ; attribValue2 ; ... ; attribNameN ; attribValueN} )
returns the value of any attribute in a 4D Write Pro range, header, body, footer, table, or document
WP Paragraph range ( targetObj ) -> Object
returns a specific range object that addresses only the paragraphs that intersect with the targetObj you passed as parameter
WP Picture range ( targetObj ) -> Object
returns a specific range object that addresses only the pictures contained in the targetObj you passed as parameter
WP SELECT ( {{* ;} wpArea;} {targetObj} {; startRange ; endRange} )
creates a new selection in the 4D Write Pro wpArea area, based upon the targetObj or a new range defined by startRange and endRange
WP USE PAGE SETUP ( wpDoc )
modifies the current printer page settings based on the 4D Write Pro document attributes for page size and orientation
WP Is font style supported ( targetObj ; wpFontStyle ) -> Boolean
returns True if the wpFontStyle style is supported by any part of the text in rangeObj
WP INSERT DOCUMENT ( targetObj ; wpDoc ; mode {; rangeUpdate} )
inserts the wpDoc document in the targetObj according to the specified insertion mode and rangeUpdate parameters
WP Get page count ( targetObj ) -> Longint
returns the total number of pages defined in the targetObj you passed in parameter
WP INSERT BREAK ( targetObj ; breakType ; mode {; rangeUpdate} )
inserts a new break of the breakType type in the targetObj according to the specified insertion mode and rangeUpdate parameters
WP NEW BOOKMARK ( targetObj ; bkName )
creates a new bookmark named bkName based upon the 4D Write Pro targetObj in the parent document
WP Bookmark range ( wpDoc ; bkName ) -> Object
returns a text range object (rangeObj) containing the range for the bookmark with the specified bkName in wpDoc
WP GET BOOKMARKS ( wpDoc ; arrBKNames )
returns an array containing the names of all bookmarks defined in wpDoc
WP DELETE BOOKMARK ( wpDoc ; bkName )
removes the bookmark named bkName from wpDoc
WP INSERT PICTURE ( targetObj ; picture ; mode {; rangeUpdate} )
inserts the picture in the targetObj according to the specified insertion mode and rangeUpdate parameter
WP Insert table ( targetObj ; mode {; rangeUpdate {; nbCols {; nbRows}}} ) -> Object
inserts a new table in the targetObj according to the specified insertion mode and returns the corresponding new table object
WP Table append row ( tableRef ; value {; value2 ; ... ; valueN} ) -> Object
appends one row to the tableRef table, fills it with value(s) and returns the corresponding row range object
WP Table get rows ( targetObj ) | ( tableRef ; startRow {; numRows} ) -> Object
returns a new cell range object containing the selection of rows from targetObj or tableRef (defined by startRow and numRows)
WP Table get columns ( targetObj ) | ( tableRef ; startCol {; numCols} ) -> Object
returns a new cell range object containing the selection of columns from targetObj or tableRef (defined by startCol and numCols)
WP Table get cells ( targetObj ) | ( tableRef ; startCol ; startRow {; numCols{; numRows}} ) -> Object
returns a new cell range object containing the selection of cells in the targetObj or tableRef (defined by startCol, startRow, numCols, and numRows)
WP Get header ( targetObj ) | (wpDoc ; sectionIndex {; subSectionType} ) -> Object
returns the header associated to the targetObj or to the specified sectionIndex of the wpDoc document
WP Get footer ( targetObj ) | (wpDoc ; sectionIndex {; sectionSubType} ) -> Object
returns the footer associated to the targetObj range or to the specified sectionIndex of the wpDoc document
WP Get body ( wpDoc ) -> Object
returns the body element of the wpDoc 4D Write Pro document
WP SET FRAME ( {* ;} wpArea ; frameSelector )
sets the cursor into the frame designated by frameSelector in the 4D Write Pro wpArea area
WP Get frame ( {* ;} wpArea ) -> Longint
returns the frame where the cursor is currently set within the 4D Write Pro wpArea area
WP Add picture ( wpDoc {; picture} ) -> Object
anchors picture at a fixed location within the wpDoc and returns its reference
WP Get element by ID ( wpDoc ; ID ) -> Object
returns an object containing the element of wpDoc passed in the ID parameter
WP Get elements ( targetObj {; elementType} ) -> Collection
returns a collection of objects containing paragraphs, images, tables and/or rows
WP Table range ( targetObj ) -> Object
returns a range object that addresses only the tables that intersect with the targetObj you passed as parameter
WP SET TEXT ( targetObj ; newText ; textPosition {; rangeUpdate} )
inserts the text passed in the newText parameter as plain text in the targetObj at the position designated by the textPosition parameter
WP Get text ( targetObj {; expressions} ) -> Text
retrieves text contents from a 4D Write Pro document within the specified targetObj
WP Get position ( targetObj {; layout} ) -> Object
returns an object describing the current position of targetObj
WP Get sections ( targetObj ) -> Collection
to be done
WP Get section ( targetObj ) | (wpDoc ; sectionIndex ) -> Object

returns first subsection intersected by the targetObj range or element, or to the specified subSectionType subsection of the wpSection section
WP New subsection ( wpSection ; subSectionType ) -> Object
creates and returns a new subsection of the subSectionType type in the wpSection 4D Write Pro section
WP DELETE SUBSECTION ( wpSection ; subSectionType )
deletes the subsection of the subSectionType type from the wpSection 4D Write Pro section
WP New header ( wpSection ) -> Object

WP New footer ( wpSection ) -> Object
creates and returns the footer associated to the section or subsection defined by the wpSection parameter
WP DELETE HEADER ( wpSection )
deletes the header element associated to the section or subsection defined by the wpSection parameter
WP DELETE FOOTER ( wpSection )
deletes the footer element associated to the section or subsection defined by the wpSection parameter
WP SET LINK ( targetObj ; linkObj )
applies a hyperlink reference to the targetObj
WP Get links ( targetObj ) -> Collection
returns the collection of all links defined in targetObj
WP SET VIEW PROPERTIES ( {* ;} wpArea ; wpViewProps )
allows you to dynamically set one or more view properties of the 4D Write Pro wpArea area
WP Get view properties ( * ; wpArea ) -> Object
returns the current view properties for the 4D Write Pro area designated by wpArea
WP New style sheet ( wpDoc ; styleSheetType ; styleSheetName ) -> Object
creates a new (empty) style sheet object for the designated wpDoc
WP DELETE STYLE SHEET ( styleSheetObj ) | (wpDoc ; styleSheetName )
removes the designated paragraph or character style sheet from the current document
WP Get style sheets ( wpDoc ; type ) -> Collection
returns a collection of all the style sheet objects of the defined type in wpDoc
WP Get style sheet ( wpDoc ; styleSheetName ) -> Object
returns the style sheet object designated by the styleSheetName
WP IMPORT STYLE SHEETS ( targetDoc ; sourceDoc )
imports all of the style sheets from the sourceDoc into the targetDoc
WP Table insert rows ( targetObj | {tableRef ; rowNumber} {; numRows} ) -> Object

WP Table insert columns ( targetObj | {tableRef ; colNumber} {; numColumns} ) -> Object
inserts one or several column(s) into a 4D Write Pro table
WP TABLE DELETE ROWS ( targetObj ) | ( tableRef ; rowNumber {; numRows} )

WP TABLE DELETE COLUMNS ( targetObj ) | ( tableRef ; colNumber {; numColumns} )

WP DELETE PICTURE ( imgObj )

WP Get formulas ( targetObj ) -> Collection
returns a collection of all formulas defined in targetObj
WP INSERT FORMULA ( targetObj ; formula ; mode {; rangeUpdate} )

WP COMPUTE FORMULAS ( targetObj )

WP FREEZE FORMULAS ( targetObj )
